  "summary": "Accenture had gone all-in as a Google Cloud partner and needed its on-prem apps rebuilt on GCP. Recreated four applications — three Hadoop / Spark-Scala / Hive pipelines scheduled by Oozie, plus one with an ML layer — as an event-driven GCP architecture: files land in Cloud Storage, Pub/Sub fires, and a Cloud Composer (Airflow) DAG runs the PySpark job on Dataproc while monitoring it, writing out to BigQuery.",
